%% Argo Workflows - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client / DSP API Server
    participant ArgoSrv as Argo Server<br/>2746/TCP HTTPS/gRPC TLS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant WFCtrl as Workflow Controller<br/>9090/TCP HTTP (metrics)
    participant WFPod as Workflow Pod<br/>(argoexec sidecar)
    participant S3 as S3/GCS/Azure<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant DB as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP TLS (optional)
    participant Prom as Prometheus

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: Workflow Execution (via CR)

    Client->>K8sAPI: POST Workflow CR<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>WFCtrl: Watch event: new Workflow<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    WFCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Pod(s) for steps<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>WFPod: Pod scheduled & started
    WFPod->>WFPod: Execute user container
    WFPod->>K8sAPI: Update Workflow status<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    WFPod->>S3: Upload artifacts<br/>Auth: Cloud credentials
    S3-->>WFPod: Artifact stored
    WFPod-->>K8sAPI: Step complete, status updated
    K8sAPI-->>WFCtrl: Watch: step completed
    WFCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create next step Pod(s)
    Note over WFCtrl,WFPod: Repeat until DAG/steps complete

    Note over Client,DB: Flow 2: API Access via Argo Server

    Client->>ArgoSrv: GET /api/v1/workflows<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / SSO JWT
    ArgoSrv->>K8sAPI: List Workflows<br/>Auth: Delegated SA Token
    K8sAPI-->>ArgoSrv: Workflow list
    ArgoSrv->>DB: Query archived workflows<br/>Auth: Username/Password
    DB-->>ArgoSrv: Archived results
    ArgoSrv-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Prom,ArgoSrv: Flow 3: Metrics Collection

    Prom->>WFCtrl: GET /metrics :9090<br/>HTTP plaintext, No Auth
    WFCtrl-->>Prom: Prometheus metrics
    Prom->>ArgoSrv: GET /metrics :2746<br/>HTTPS TLS, Bearer Token
    ArgoSrv-->>Prom: Prometheus metrics
